In their own words.



Breigh
Administrative Assistant

I absolutely love my Supervisors. I feel that I’m learning new things on a daily basis.  It’s a very happy, family like work environment,  and that makes it a pleasure to come to work every day.  I’m very fortunate to have such a great job and to be able to work with these great people. 



Michelle
Tank Truck Driver 

I like working for Select Energy Services because of the friendly and family like atmosphere. The drivers here are excellent when it comes to team work and helping each other out. Also the benefits that Select Energy Services offers are a great bonus!



Daniel
Tank Truck Driver

I enjoy working for Select Energy Services, because it is the closest thing I can compare to the type of “family” I had while serving in the Military. Working in an environment, where everyone works together and helps each other out in an effort to make sure we ALL look and perform our best for our customers. As soon as I walked in, I immediately felt like there was potential to move up and that it is encouraged to strive for more and do your best to achieve whatever your goal might be. Between the excellent command team, and the top-notch employees that support them, there is not a better example of a superior company in the gas and oil business.



