Well Testing & Flowback – Select Energy Services| Select Energy Services





























































Well Testing & Flowback

Select’s Well Testing and Flowback services provide solutions with regionally specialized equipment and knowledge spanning the national footprint. Our state-of-the-art inventory of equipment meets American Petroleum Institute (API) standards and enables us to safely meet all of your well requirements.  Our highly trained and experienced flowback and well test operators can safely and effectively operate in all testing situations, including high-risk environments such as high temperature, high pressure, and high concentrations of H2S. We also offer trained and experienced pumping personnel to assist with production once the well has been completed.
