EQUIPMENT:
Our inventory of equipment meets API standards and enables us to safely meet all of your well testing requirements. Both our equipment and experienced team members can safely and effectively operate in all testing environments, including high-risk environments such as high temperature, high pressure, and/or high concentrations of H2S (sour gas).
